sellerCard.oneLiner: Let us create a professional website together
sellerCard.description:
Hy, I am Aneel, I have more than 9 years of experience in wordpress website development and have been serving the local community since 2013.

i am happy to help you with the website project you desire . i am a diligent and dedicated person

Feel free to contact with me.. Cheers!

description.content:
Are you in need of a professional and modern WordPress website for your business? Look no further! I am a web developer with years of experience in creating high-quality webs for businesses of all sizes.


I specialize in custom website design and development using the latest technologies and design trends, ensuring that your website is not only visually appealing but also responsive, easy to navigate, and optimized for search engines.


My services include:


  • Custom WordPress theme design and development tailored for construction industry / Real Estate business / music websites / fashion industry / restaurant portal and much more.


  • Drag and drop function (Divi / visual composer / Elementor / beaver builder / themify builder / seedprod / Custom).


  • E-commerce web development.


  • Website optimization for search engines.


  • maintenance and updates.


  • Mobile optimization.


  • Topnotch security.


We offer a lifetime of FREE Web Maintenance Services after development/ launching. Let's work together to bring your business online and start reaching new customers today!"

questionsAndAnswers.question: My Website will be Search engine optimization (SEO) ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
Yes , for this we ..

--> will add SEO Yoast plugin and configer 
--> will add Site Map in website
--> configure website with google console
--> Will add schema.org

will provide you proper document for this ..

questionsAndAnswers.question: My Website will be load Fast or Slow ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Your website will be load very fast , after complete website we will work on speed optimization and will provide you 80 to 90 points in speed optimization from 100

questionsAndAnswers.question: My Website will be Responsive for Mobiles ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: yes , your website will be responsive for all mobiles and tablets we will Create a responsive , cross browser/platform design for your site

questionsAndAnswers.question: If a face Issue in website in future then you will charged ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: No , if you face any issue in futer after complete project we will provide you our services free of cast in priority basis

questionsAndAnswers.question: What About my Website Security ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Your Website will be fully secure and will not hack or will not down will guarantee for this .. we will add Security plugin for this and will provide you proper document

questionsAndAnswers.question: Does your gig cost include Hosting & Domain too ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: No, you will have to provide me Hosting & Domain.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can You copy a website and convert to WordPress?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: yes, but please contact me in inbox to discuss.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you Work With Bootstrap 3 Or Mobile Friendly Website ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: yes, but please contact me in inbox and discuss the order requirements.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you make custom websites based on my requirement ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: yes, but please contact me in inbox and discuss the order requirements with me before placing the order

questionsAndAnswers.question: How can edit my website in future ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: we will provide you hand written document for this with screenshots. and your website back-end will be very user friendly

reviews.comment: Aneel was a pleasant to work with and always polite.  He was very diligent and always wanted to please me. Although he hadn't worked with Siteground previously, he reviewed my account and determined he could. He provided a prolific list of referrals so I could identify which formats I preferred and I provided ones to him. He also gave me access to his photo inventory. He considered my preferences when creating my website. The challenges were communicating to him photo changes and text placement. The project took longer than I had hoped due to these challenges. He has a lifetime guarantee of his work, which is certainly above and beyond.  I would hire him again because I know now that he understands visual examples of what I want better than just writing out directions.

Incredible! He built an amazing website and customized it exactly how I wanted it. Throughout the process, I made many requests for changes and he made all of them for me. He was extremely patient, professional and did fantastic work. I'm 100% happy and impressed with the website he built for me. It is truly one of the best values I've ever received. I've already referred him to people I know and will continue to do so. Thank you!

Aneel is an OUTSTANDING website developer! His professionalism, attention to detail, and code expertise shine through in every project, and his proactive communication and politeness make working with him a breeze. He consistently goes above and beyond—such a helpful, supportive partner with quick turnaround times 🙌; looking forward to collaborating even more!
This was a great gig.  Exactly what I had hoped for!

WOW! Outstanding work. He's my go-to web-guy now! 
Super fast 
Awesome quality
Easy to work with
A "Dream" web-guy!
